T1  - Retaining alpha: The effect of trade size and rebalancing frequency on FX strategy returns
AU  - Melvin, Michael
AU  - Pan, Wenqiang
AU  - Wikstrom, Petra
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 51
SP  - 100545
